                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8327" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1284</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1670 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“放卫星式”的“狂飙”开店：库迪能否再造咖啡神话</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Rapid opening of shops&quot; in the &quot;satellite&quot; style: Can COTTI COFFEE recreate the coffee myth?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">谭庆美，邵楠</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">库迪咖啡（北京）有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">库迪咖啡；联营模式；比附定位；营销组合策略</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">COTTI COFFEE; Joint venture model; Comparative positioning; Marketing mix strategies</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022年10月开出第一家门店，仅成立一年便完成超6000家门店的布局，业务覆盖全球28个国家及地区，崭露头角的库迪咖啡凭借其“放卫星式”的“狂飙”扩店速度和低价营销被广泛关注。在历时一年多的经营发展过程中，库迪咖啡以创新的联营模式，风险共担、利润分成的商业逻辑，出色的产品创新，新颖的跨界联名，多样的中国元素融入，高性价比的消费体验，不断努力为咖啡市场和消费者带来惊喜和新鲜感。本案例描述了库迪咖啡自成立以来的创业发展历程和一系列营销策略，讲述其如何带着再造咖啡神话的“野心”在当前竞争激烈的咖啡市场迅速赢得一席之地，以及在快速拓店过程中所面临的困难和挑战。旨在帮助学生理解联营模式、比附定位和营销组合策略的相关理论和应用，同时为初创企业选择合适的扩张模式和营销策略提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the first shop opening in October 2022, and the layout of over 6,000 shops completed in just one year after its establishment, with business covering 28 countries and regions around the world, the emerging COTTI Coffee has been widely noticed for its amazing &quot;satellite&quot; speed of shop expansion and low-priced marketing strategy. In the course of more than a year&#39;s operation and development, COTTI Coffee has continuously endeavored to bring surprises and freshness to the coffee market and consumers with its innovative Joint venture model, risk-sharing and profit-sharing business logic, outstanding product innovation, novel cross-border co-branding, diversified integration of Chinese elements, and cost-effective consumer experience. This case describes the entrepreneurial development and a series of marketing strategies of COTTI Coffee since its establishment, and tells it how to win a place quickly in the current competitive coffee market with the “ambition” of re-creating the coffee myth, as well as the difficulties and challenges it faced in the process of rapidly expanding its shops. The aim is to assist students in understanding relevant theories and applications of joint venture models, comparative positioning and marketing mix strategies, as well as provide lessons for start-ups in choosing appropriate expansion models and marketing strategies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">联营模式；比附定位；4P营销组合理论；烧钱式营销</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-05</td>
                            </tr>
